# ziffy

A ZFS command line utility to browse and rescue damaged pools using low level API calls.

## Installation

```shell
pip install ziffy
```

## Examples

Root privileges are likely required to access the disks.

```shell
sudo python -m ziffy datasets <pool-name>
```

